my work to you.

369
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,800
I understand.

370
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:57,280
Is receiving the On-the-Rise Award
worth it? It isn’t.

371
00:22:57,360 --> 00:22:58,440
We’re talking about
your health here.

372
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:01,440
