my work at all.

373
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:04,840
I’ve explained it to you
so many times.

374
00:23:05,040 --> 00:23:06,720
This is how I work.

375
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:09,840
It’s never been a problem before,
so why is it a problem now?

376
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:12,760
