391
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,760
No.

392
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,080
Why live separately?

393
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:02,600
I'm sorry.

394
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,240
